ngs towards wildlife. Working together with journalists by engaging in dialogue and exchanging experiences should be central in future conservation management.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Nanni, Veronica", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mammola, Stefano", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mac\u00edas-Hern\u00e1ndez, Nuria", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Castrogiovanni, Alessia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Salgado, Ana L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lunghi, Enrico", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ficetola, Gentile Francesco", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Modica, Corrado", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Alba, Riccardo", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Spiriti, Maria Michela", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Holtze, Susanne", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "De Mello, \u00c9rica Munhoz", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "De Mori, Barbara", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Biasetti, Pierfrancesco", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chamberlain, Dan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Manenti, Raoul", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/b02614f93d313375d48df1b1c09b08dc", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/a2381dd9d5854b519f4bd59a8a54e9dd8addf24a71dedb4a6f4b96f216607af7", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/R7I85FF8", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/R7I85FF8", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/75d1f465d7cd12c94539c4bcf196fb07!/b266171-268632", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": 